    SELECT [t0].[ParentId], [t0].[Id], [x.Products0].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [Products] AS [x.Products0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [x1].[ParentId], [x1].[Id]
        FROM [ProductCategories] AS [x1]
    ) AS [t0] ON [x.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [x.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t1].[Id0]
ORDER BY [t1].[ParentId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[DateCreated], [p2].[Id]
    FROM [Products] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p.ProductCategory2] ON [p2].[CategoryId] = [p.ProductCategory2].[Id]
    WHERE [p2].[Status] = 1
    ORDER BY [p2].[DateCreated] DESC, [p2].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t2] ON [p.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[DateCreated] DESC, [t2].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
